name: Hipster Laocoon
description: An animation based on one of the real marble statue of the artist Leo Caillard. The statue named " Hipster Laocoon" is inspired by the famous "Laocoon" statue from the ancient Greek era . Leo Caillard carves Sunglasses and Hat out of the marble to make it look familiar and connected to the present. Leo Caillard plays with the time and connect together different historical period in his creations. It's the first of his NFT's and the beginning of a serie of 5 different NFT's presenting monumental " Hipster " statues in natural environment that will be released every 3 weeks.
